      <odd id="aspace_5a4e7f1b9a3aba8bd23e0896820d4eea">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 38-B (YRG 38-B), Records documenting specific sports at Yale.</p>  
      </odd>
      <altformavail id="aspace_3619d35c81996a9887129f15ff4776a1">
         <head>Existence and Location of Copies</head>
         <p>Boxing scrapbooks are available on microfilm from Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library, at cost. Order no. HM183. 1984. 2095 frames on 3 reels, 35mm.</p>  
      </altformavail>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_16dbb3e1548e4f373b7091a4f79cdb09">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The materials were transferred from the Department of Athletics, 2005.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_57d795da2f0977754c8bc5cb2304871e">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Patrons must use HM FILM 183 instead of the original scrapbooks.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_3f103c11cbb642356d38d46476a4a7b0">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Yale University Athletic Association Scrapbooks Documenting Boxing (RU 936), Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_7569f6f2f615542411136277605cdca1">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged chronologically.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_9825cd166ee7f184d37f52e78fe95a97">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of scrapbooks maintained by the Yale University Athletic Association (later known as the Department of Athletics, Physical Education, and Recreation) documenting boxing at Yale.</p>  
